---
title: Honey Mustard Beef Burgers with Easy Beetroot Relish & Aioli
description: We thought it was time to upgrade the classic beef burger. With a sweet caramelised beetroot relish, honey and mustard beef patties and creamy garlic aioli, this humble takeaway staple is all grown up and ready to party!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-burgers-beetroot-aioli-a2e1a03a.jpg
